node.text: From reefs to ridges, explore the beauty of the Philippines through the eyes of the locals. While 2020 has been a year of change for travel, the Philippines is excited to invite local visitors to explore the beautiful islands. The #BDTeam had the pleasure of working with @tourism_phl to highlight beautiful places around the Philippines. The opportunities for exploration are endless-from the Hundred Island National Park in Pangasinan to exploring the Suba and Culili Sand Dunes in Ilocos Norte.

node.text:
With an incredibly rich history, being an “Egyptian” can have many facets especially when it comes to creativity. Today, we’re sharing a unique story dedicated to any creative who intends to carve their own path no matter the circumstances. 

“It’s proof that the end product most of the time doesn’t pan out the way you expect it. And its by having expectations that you hinder your potential.” - @matiasderada

Watch this beautiful film on Beautiful Destinations Youtube channel. 🇪🇬

🎥 @matiasderada #BDTeam

Bristol Bay, one of Alaska’s most treasured natural wonders, is under threat. @world_wildlife 

It’s home to an irreplaceable ecosystem and one of the last salmon strongholds. Not only that, its iconic wildlife has sprung up a sustainable tourism industry which effects thousands of Alaskan livelihoods.

All of this is under threat if the Pebble Mine moves forward. The recent approval of the environmental impact statement has made it clear that our voices need to be heard. 

Nature and people can’t live without fresh water, and Bristol Bay is the lifeblood that sustains every species calling the region home. 

On a recent trip to Alaska, the #BDTeam and WWF Ambassador, @jeremyjauncey, learned firsthand about the conservation community’s fight against Pebble Mine.

node.text: As New York City starts to open back up, we wanted to take a moment to reflect on the efforts of heroes in the hospitality industry who have been helping our frontline workers. @fsnewyork was the first hotel in New York City to open its door to our frontline workers and provide them with a safe haven to stay during such an uncertain time. They quickly transformed the hotel into a near medical-grade facility. Over 300 medical workers called @fsnewyork home during this time as they were provided rooms free of charge. This allowed them to keep their own families safe as they focused on their work and taking care of patients. ❤️ (🎥: @loganlambert 📸: @loganstrongarms 📍: Four Seasons Hotel New York)

node.text:
These endless flower fields shot by @nick_skeyes are currently what we're daydreaming about. When in the Netherlands, you must pay a visit to one of their breathtaking tulip fields. 🌷

The tulip season usually spans from the end of March until mid-May during springtime, but the flowers are usually at their prime halfway through April. Witnessing millions of tulips blooming is truly a spectacle, especially with that colors range from red, pink, white, yellow, and purple. 😍

Does this make you want to plan a trip to the Netherlands? Where do you think are the most beautiful tulip fields in the world? 🇳🇱

📸 @nick_skeyes
📍 Holland, Netherlands

Nature's playground at @visitrasalkhaimah. 🔥 Nestled in the mountains of Ras Al Khaimah lies Wadi Sha'ah, an incredible moderate-to-hard hiking destination that will please experienced hikers and outdoor enthusiasts. 🇦🇪

If you're in for an adrenaline-packed adventure in the UAE, you must make your way to Wadi Sha'ah. Presenting unique hiking challenges, it features boulder hopping, scree slopes, dry waterfalls, donkey trails, and rugged paths. A good level of fitness is required to conquer the 13km full-circuit trail, so planning and preparing for the hike is a must. 👌🏼

Would you take a hike here and have you visited Ras Al Khaimah yet?

📽 @reme_martyr, @tomjauncey, @faisalriazkhan
📍 Wadi Sha'ah, @visitrasalkhaimah, UAE

Underwater dreaming with @shellseaflmermaid via @themikerioux. 🧜‍♀️ Besides the pristine water and swarm of fish in this natural Florida spring, the manatee's surprise appearance makes this footage even more incredible. 🇺🇸

Manatees are curious by nature and often initiate interaction with humans; so if you happen to see manatees while swimming, snorkeling, diving, or boating, it's important to avoid doing anything disruptive. You can "look but don't touch" while practicing passive observation from a distance, avoid excessive noise and splashing, and resist the urge to feed them. (source: savethemanatee.org) ✔️

Have you ever seen a manatee before? 😍

📽 @themikerioux
🧜‍♀️ @shellseaflmermaid
📍 Florida, US
🎶 Kathleen - Pure Imagination

Paradise found by @johnderting. 🌎 Leave it to this footage to give you your daily dose of relaxation. 😌

In the Wrangell Mountains of Alaska, mid-summer glacier water cuts channels through solid ice. This showcases an absolute dream of unspoiled wilderness: crystal clear water, curving river valleys, and towering mountains on the horizon. 🏔

Have you ever thought of exploring Alaska? 🇺🇸

📽 @johnderting
📍 Wrangell Mountains, Alaska
🎶 James Horner - Hymn To The Sea

Chasing waterfalls and rainbows with @settemsdal. 🌈 Check out this incredible perspective of the “The Seven Sisters” waterfall in Norway! 😍

Comprised of seven waterfalls with an average fall of 250 meters, The Seven Sisters is one of the most photographed waterfalls in Geirangerfjorden. One of the best ways to see the sight is by boat and the most ideal time to visit is during May-July during the snow melting period, when the falls are naturally more visible. 🇳🇴

Is Norway a dream destination of yours? If yes, what makes you want to travel here?

📽 @settemsdal
📍 The Seven Sisters Waterfall, Norway
🎶 In This Shirt - The Irrepressibles

Did you know this surreal oasis is found in Egypt and would you take a dip here? 🤯

A bar with a view via @fashioninmysoul. 🍸 With a rooftop terrace like this, you can get the best of Prague in the palm of your hand. 😍

When in the capital of the Czech Republic, you must try dining and relaxing in one of its many rooftop restaurants and bars. Enjoy delicious cuisine, great conversations, and amazing views of the Old Town Square, Tyn Cathedral, Prague Castle, Petřín Tower, and more iconic landmarks. 🇨🇿

Have you been to Prague and do you have any suggestions on the best rooftop spaces to visit? ✨

📽 @fashioninmysoul
📍 Prague, Czech Republic
🎶 Lily James - A Dream is a Wish Your Heart Makes

Barcelona from night to day via @world_walkerz. ✨ Set on the country's northeastern coast, Barcelona is the cosmopolitan capital of Spain’s Catalonia region and is known for its wealth of art and impressive architecture. 🇪🇸

If you're planning a visit, bookmark this and add these items to your bucket list! 📝

𝟭𝟬 𝗕𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝗧𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴𝘀 𝘁𝗼 𝗗𝗼 𝗶𝗻 𝗕𝗮𝗿𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗼𝗻𝗮
1. Tour La Sagrada Família.
2. Marvel at Casa Batlló.
3. Feast on a food tour at La Boqueria. 
4. Enjoy green space at Parc del Laberint d'Horta. 
5. Discover masterpieces at the Picasso Museum.
6. Stroll the famous street of La Rambla. 
7. Explore the Palau de la Música Catalana.
8. Hang out in the seaside locale of La Barceloneta.
9. Shop at Portal del Angel or Passeig de Gracia.
10. Go on a night out at El Born.

Is there anything missing from our list? Share your suggestions! 🧐

📸 @world_walkerz
📍 Barcelona, Spain
